    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/7e9131fd732988c2fa5e56c2eb9c4fea.poster.avif?t=1729500716\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/7e9131fd732988c2fa5e56c2eb9c4fea.webm?t=1729500716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/7e9131fd732988c2fa5e56c2eb9c4fea.mp4?t=1729500716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Short Memories</strong> 是一个非常短的游戏，讲述了两个女人在长椅上讨论的故事。这个游戏旨在<strong>将衰老和变老正常化</strong>。你将通过对话引导的不同小游戏，了解老年生活的不同方面。<br><br>变老及其所有含义是生活中非常正常的一部分。Short Memories 试图避免讨论我们在生命阶段中害怕的事情（如疾病、死亡或其他困难），而是展示两个正在经历这一阶段的人，进行一场普通的对话。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/77aa7c364e404d682d2b591082aedd78.poster.avif?t=1729500716\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/77aa7c364e404d682d2b591082aedd78.webm?t=1729500716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/77aa7c364e404d682d2b591082aedd78.mp4?t=1729500716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏仅通过鼠标操作，你需要完成3个小游戏才能到达终点。这些小游戏各有其难度，尝试传达老年人可能遇到的困难。这些都通过笨拙的游戏机制进行展示。<br><br>你还将跟随我们的两位女士，在她们最喜欢的长椅上进行的简短对话，讨论生活的过去、现在和未来。<br><br>希望你喜欢 <strong>Short Memories</strong>，它是用<strong>爱</strong>制作的！<br><br>✨✨✨<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/cd37ad96fdb0795f73ff43d6c12d8312.poster.avif?t=1729500716\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/cd37ad96fdb0795f73ff43d6c12d8312.webm?t=1729500716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189110/extras/cd37ad96fdb0795f73ff43d6c12d8312.mp4?t=1729500716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
